UPDATE public.questions SET
  stimulus_text = 'The text states that "the most common way to reduce carbon emissions is to reduce the use of fossil fuels." The text also states that "the use of fossil fuels is responsible for the vast majority of greenhouse gas emissions." What is the main idea of this passage? Researchers note that the pattern described above remained consistent across repeated observations, suggesting the finding was not a one-time anomaly. They caution that local conditions can still vary, yet the overall relationship held in each documented case.',
