UPDATE public.questions SET
  stimulus_text = 'Many people, including historians, have been fascinated by the impact of technological change on societies. Although the impact of technology on society is often seen as a positive, it can have a negative effect, especially when a new technology is introduced into a society without much thought being given to its impact. For example, the introduction of new technologies to societies where traditional methods have been used for generations can have a negative impact on the environment.  Such environmental degradation, however, can be avoided by carefully considering the impact of new technologies before they are introduced. 

