UPDATE public.questions SET
  stimulus_text = 'The author provides a history of the process of how the United States obtained the Louisiana Purchase.  The author also states that the Louisiana Purchase was a key moment in American history because it doubled the size of the United States.  The author argues that the Louisiana Purchase was also a pivotal event because it helped to open up the western part of the United States to settlement.  The author concludes by saying that the Louisiana Purchase is a significant event in American history. What is the main idea of this passage?',
